@startuml sd_PayslipService_generateHtml
skinparam backgroundColor #F9FAFB
title PayslipService.generateHtml(recordId) - 生成HTML工资条预览

actor "调用方" as Client
participant "PayslipController" as Ctrl
participant "PayslipService" as PSlipSvc
participant "SalaryRecordRepository" as RecRepo
participant "SalaryItemRepository" as ItemRepo
participant "ObjectMapper" as OM

Client -> Ctrl: GET /api/payslips/{id}/html
Ctrl -> PSlipSvc: generateHtml(recordId)
PSlipSvc -> RecRepo: findById(recordId)
RecRepo --> PSlipSvc: SalaryRecord
PSlipSvc -> OM: readValue(itemValues, Map)
OM --> PSlipSvc: Map<String, Double>
PSlipSvc -> ItemRepo: findByActiveTrueOrderBySortOrder()
ItemRepo --> PSlipSvc: List<SalaryItem> → codeNameMap
note right of PSlipSvc #F0F8FF
  **构建HTML字符串:**
  <html>
    <h2>工资条</h2>
    <table> 员工信息 </table>
    <table border=1>
      <tr> 项目 | 金额 </tr>
      loop明细...
      <tr> 应发合计 </tr>
      <tr> 个税 / 社保/ 公积金 </tr>
      <tr style=red> 实发合计 </tr>
    </table>
  </html>
end note
PSlipSvc --> Ctrl: String (完整HTML代码)
Ctrl --> Client: ApiResponse<String>\n(前端直接innerHTML渲染)
@enduml
